.opencode/specs/deep-loops/034-gpt-reliability-research/research/iterations/iter-010.md:11:3. GPT stalls on multi-step prose protocols that allow long dark windows. The council protocol says to “Dispatch or simulate distinct seats within one CLI round,” then critique, then persist artifacts only in phase 4 (`.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/references/integration/loop_protocol.md:22-27`, `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-ai-council/references/integration/loop_protocol.md:98-120`). Packet 033 shows GPT-high still silently stalled on ACB-004 and ACB-005, while Claude passed ACB-004 (`.opencode/specs/deep-loops/033-deep-loop-behavior-benchmarks/004-rollout-council-improvement/scorecard.md:18-19`, `.opencode/specs/deep-loops/033-deep-loop-behavior-benchmarks/004-rollout-council-improvement/scorecard.md:42-50`).
.opencode/specs/deep-loops/034-gpt-reliability-research/research/iterations/iter-010.md:23:3. **Stepwise Liveness**. **Change:** Add heartbeat/progress records after each seat, critique, and referee step; retrofit council protocol and auto YAML before changing budgets. **Expected effect:** Addresses measured structured-mode stalls where high effort did not help (`004-rollout-council-improvement/scorecard.md:42-50`). **Effort:** M. **Risk:** Medium; partial states need cleanup semantics.
.opencode/specs/deep-loops/034-gpt-reliability-research/research/iterations/iter-003.md:11:5. The benchmark catches the failure by comparing independent signals: task events are scraped from transcript dispatch lines (`.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/shared/behavior-benchmark/behavior-bench-run.cjs:656-668`), route-proof is scraped from fixture `*state.jsonl` files (`:416-456`), and `role_absorption` is assigned when work products appear without delegation evidence (`:337-366`). `RSB-007-med` shows the exact divergence: `tFirstDispatchMs: null`, `taskEvents: []`, a matching `deep-research` route-proof record, and `classification: "role_absorption"` (`.opencode/specs/deep-loops/033-deep-loop-behavior-benchmarks/003-rollout-research-context/runs/gpt-fast-med/RSB-007-gpt-fast-med.result.json:7-24`, `:53-59`). `RSB-005-med` shows no dispatch/proof and hard timeout (`.opencode/specs/deep-loops/033-deep-loop-behavior-benchmarks/003-rollout-research-context/runs/gpt-fast-med/RSB-005-gpt-fast-med.result.json:7-17`, `:33-43`).
